91
00:04:59,780 --> 00:05:00,420
Qingyan.

92
00:05:03,060 --> 00:05:03,660
Come on.

93
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:09,180
Lingzhi,

94
00:05:12,940 --> 00:05:14,460
I didn't betray you.

95
00:05:16,180 --> 00:05:17,940
I didn't say anything.

96
00:05:19,580 --> 00:05:20,460
